name: THC Thai High Cannabis - Patong, Phuket
description: T.H.C Thai High Corporation based in the middle of beach road in Patong in Phuket supplies exotic / top shelf cannabis, edibles, cigars and high quality smoking accessories. This is a must visit location for any cannabis enthusiasts or people curious to learn more about cannabis from T.H.C’s friendly knowledgable staff.
